{"word":"καταδιαιτάω","slug":"καταδιαιτάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n53906\" key=\"katadiaita/w\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">καταδῐαιτάω</orth>, <sense id=\"n53906.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">decide as arbitrator against</tr_> one, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give judgement against</tr_>, opp. <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀποδ-, ὁ διαιτητὴς οὐ κατεδιῄτα, ἀλλ᾽ ἀπιὼν ᾤχετο ἀποδιαιτήσας τούτου τὴν δίαιταν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg049.perseus-grc1:19\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">49.19</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:84\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.84</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οἷός τ᾽ ἦν πείθειν αὐτόν, ἣν κατεδεδιῃτήκει, ταύτην ἀποδεδιῃτημένην ἀποφαίνειν</foreign> ib.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">85</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἔρημον κ. τινὸς</foreign> [<foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">δίκην</foreign>] <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">give judgement</tr_> in default <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">against</tr_> one, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg021.perseus-grc1:92\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Id.\">Id.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">21.92</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg040.perseus-grc1:17\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">40.17</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0062.tlg040:15\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">